{"tid":2370660,"cid":36,"subCid":0,"title":"頸椎有抽搐感 但未到刺痛","createTime":"2021-01-18T07:53:08.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-18T08:37:18.000Z","uid":30673,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"23224a30e0ad81783ae00c414d71d97843866479","tid":2370660,"uid":30673,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-18T07:53:08.000Z","msg":"呢一個禮拜由軟床褥轉左硬床褥<br />\n第一日訓已經覺得背脊唔多自然 但冇理<br />\n之後就黎料 而家用返平時姿勢用電腦果陣<br />\n一靠前/托頭就覺得頸椎個位抽下抽下 <br />\n一直挨後就冇事 訓教就feel到背脊兩個突位抽<br />\n<br />\n問題就黎 其實張硬床褥我訓左差唔多10年 係上年先轉軟訓左一年 而家再訓返硬<br />\n到底係張軟嘅訓到我k左型 定係我本身應該訓軟<br />\n同埋想睇嘅話係咪鐵打最好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"314774624b789d7c0e39f6163231fa54d01ec7ab","tid":2370660,"uid":355310,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-18T07:56:08.000Z","msg":"我自己覺得軟點都好過硬，條脊椎彎㗎嘛"},{"pid":"a7c48ee601cc2ab23add6a4536a939872dd32072","tid":2370660,"uid":228894,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-18T08:00:14.000Z","msg":"叫基爾獸幫你捽吓條頸"},{"pid":"2bf07e70cd5b39d9aebf21d7c31b6a8526b77230","tid":2370660,"uid":30673,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"314774624b789d7c0e39f6163231fa54d01ec7ab","tid":2370660,"uid":355310,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-18T07:56:08.000Z","msg":"我自己覺得軟點都好過硬，條脊椎彎㗎嘛"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-18T08:35:07.000Z","msg":"但之前訓咁耐都冇事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0ab360da49d25227b78bcd50d05d1e9e21e79c36","tid":2370660,"uid":355310,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2bf07e70cd5b39d9aebf21d7c31b6a8526b77230","tid":2370660,"uid":30673,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"314774624b789d7c0e39f6163231fa54d01ec7ab","tid":2370660,"uid":355310,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-18T07:56:08.000Z","msg":"我自己覺得軟點都好過硬，條脊椎彎㗎嘛"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-18T08:35:07.000Z","msg":"但之前訓咁耐都冇事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoj